I think the premise is good, but your ideas are very, very powerful--a bit too strong, in my estimation.<P>As far as I'm concerned, the easiest and most effective fix is to make pets immune to ripostes. I honestly cannot imagine this overpowering any pet class, since no pet can tank an uber mob, ripostes or not. If you can't make the pet immune to riposts in general, code it so that mobs of level 55 or higher (could probably do level 60 or higher, too) don't riposte on pets at all.<P>--------------------<P>That a man is a great warrior may not be measured by how many lives he has taken.<P>He is great in that, no matter how many fall before his blade, each is regretted as the first was.
